Class PersistentLicense

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.forgerock.openam.license.License
      • org.forgerock.openam.license.PersistentLicense
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable
    public class PersistentLicense
extends License
    A License that remembers whether the user has accepted it or not in a persistent log file, to avoid prompting the user to accept the license more than once.

    12.0.0
